Challenge 328
- Task 1 (Replace all ?): fill '?' to avoid consecutive duplicates; see perl/ch-1.pl and python/ch-1.py.
- Task 2 (Good String): remove opposite-case adjacent pairs until stable; see perl/ch-2.pl and python/ch-2.py.

Run inline tests:
- Perl: `perl perl/ch-1.pl` and `perl perl/ch-2.pl`
- Python: `python3 python/ch-1.py` and `python3 python/ch-2.py`
